_sText:
This is my first map. I decided to keep it simple. However, I did add a secret. On the terrorist team, hit the button next to spawn, then, go left towards the ramp hit E on the end of the crate right next to the ramp. Walk to the end of the inside of the crate. You will be teleported to a box of which you can see out of but the other players can't see in. There is also an awp in that box.

If you read the notes, this benefited you.
